      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Ladies and gentlemen, our nation stands at a crossroads. The values that have built our great country are under attack by modern progressive radicals who seek to redefine family, marriage, and personal responsibility. We must stand firm and protect the sanctity of traditional family values. Our children deserve to be raised in homes where fathers and mothers are the primary caregivers, and where the family is the foundation of society. We cannot allow the radical left to erode the bedrock of our nation, which is built upon the love, dedication, and unity of a traditional family. Together, we will fight to preserve these timeless principles and ensure that our country remains strong, united, and true to its heritage. Thank you.",
